### Add a New Medicine (Tablet)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/medicines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Paracetamol",
  "category": "Tablet",
  "price": 5.50,
  "stockQuantity": 100,
  "requiresPrescription": false,
  "manufacturer": "PharmaCorp"
}

### Get All Medicines
GET http://localhost:8080/api/medicines